5449/http://www.oregonlive.com/business/index.ssf/2010/01/air_canada_to_launch_direct_se.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在并购西北航空之后，达美航空维持着往[[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]和[[东京|东京]]的直飞航班。在2009年到2010年的冬春交际期间，[[波特兰港|波特兰港]]向[[达美航空|达美航空]]支付了350万美元的补贴，以维持东京航线的运营。<ref>{{cite news|title=Keeping the Routes Open|url=http://www.oregonlive.com/opinion/index.ssf/2010/06/keeping_the_routes_open.html|newspaper=[[The_Oregonian|The Oregonian]]|location=Portland|date=June 18, 2010|accessdate=June 18, 2010|archive-date=2010-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100627114517/http://www.oregonlive.com/opinion/index.ssf/2010/06/keeping_the_routes_open.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

